.SH NAME
backlight_force_update \- tell the backlight subsystem that hardware state has changed
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" backlight_force_update
.BI "(struct backlight_device *bd "  ","
.BI "enum backlight_update_reason reason "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "bd" 12
the backlight device to update
.IP "reason" 12
reason for update
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Updates the internal state of the backlight in response to a hardware event,
and generates an uevent to notify userspace. A backlight driver shall call
\fBbacklight_force_update\fP when the backlight is changed using, for example,
a hot-key. The updated brightness is read using \fBget_brightness\fP and the
brightness value is reported using an uevent.
